title: Kubernetes: Pod Phase
agents: kubernetes
catalog: containerization/kubernetes
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check shows the phase of a Pod, which Kubernetes defines to be a simple, high-level summary of
 where the Pod is in its lifecycle. The service always displays an {OK} state regardless of the
 current phase.

 It requires that the special agent kube is configured.
discovery:
 One service is created for each Pod.
